<p>Alessandra is already well known in her native Puerto Rico, boasting 677,000 Instagram followers and hosting her own show 'Dare with Alessandra'.</p>

<p>Born in San Juan, Puerto Rico, Alessandra was educated in the US and holds a master's degree in marriage and family therapy.</p>

<p>She is now a clinical sexologist with over 20 years of experience and has authored a number of published books.</p>

